citation.case_name: In the Matter of James Cally. No. D-807. Former Decision, 492 U.S. 941, 110 S.CT. 32. June 11, 1990. It Having Been Reported to the Court That James J. Cally Has Died, the Rule to Show Cause, Heretofore, Issued on September 25, 1989, is Hereby Discharged

html:
496 U.S. 922

110 S.Ct. 2613

110 L.Ed.2d 635

In the Matter of James CALLY.
No. D-807.
Former decision, 492 U.S. 941, 110 S.Ct. 32.
June 11, 1990. It having been reported to the Court that James J. Cally has died, The Rule to Show Cause, heretofore, issued on September 25, 1989, is hereby discharged.
